#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1448
msgid ""
"We will miss $deadguy.name|, but at least she was not one of our experienced "
"troops!"
msgstr ""
"Недостајаће нам $deadguy.name|, али бар не беше једна од наши искусних "
"јединица!"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1463
msgid ""
"Losing a healer hurts all the troops! Keep them out of the enemy’s reach!"
msgstr ""
"Губитак видара штети свим нашим снагама! Чувај га ван дохвата непријатеља!"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/2_Tutorial.cfg:1464
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "<big>Tracking Enemy Movement</big>"
